WEBVTT

01:39.590 --> 01:43.340
[Road to Success]

01:44.690 --> 01:47.910
[Episode 20]

02:38.590 --> 02:40.120
Don't let what happened to Jason

02:40.120 --> 02:41.910
happen to another child.

02:42.610 --> 02:44.410
Take good care of your students.

03:25.660 --> 03:31.300
[Little Savage Tribe]

03:28.160 --> 03:30.950
All players, gather at the school field.

03:34.750 --> 03:35.750
Why do you think

03:35.750 --> 03:37.440
Coach called us here so late at night?

03:37.440 --> 03:38.610
He loves us too much.

03:38.770 --> 03:40.430
Coach is here.

03:40.430 --> 03:41.500
Hello, Coach.

03:41.520 --> 03:42.790
-Hello, Coach.
-Coach.

03:42.790 --> 03:44.680
-Hello, Coach.
-Hello, Coach.

03:44.680 --> 03:45.840
Coach,

03:45.840 --> 03:47.079
calling us here so late,

03:47.079 --> 03:48.560
it can't be for training, right?

03:48.560 --> 03:49.680
We're all dressed up.

03:49.680 --> 03:51.140
How can we train like this?

03:52.960 --> 03:54.120
It's not training.

03:55.680 --> 03:56.810
Then why are we here?

03:59.560 --> 04:00.290
Just to chat.

04:00.710 --> 04:01.310
-A chat.
-OK.

04:01.310 --> 04:02.190
Who cares?

04:02.190 --> 04:03.720
-A chat!
-Let's have a chat.

04:06.710 --> 04:07.580
Coach,

04:07.610 --> 04:09.300
why are you so shy today?

04:09.320 --> 04:10.510
Have a seat, Coach.

04:10.900 --> 04:11.980
Have a seat, Coach.

04:22.620 --> 04:23.900
First of all, I want to

04:23.930 --> 04:25.200
reintroduce myself.

04:28.370 --> 04:29.400
I'm Wang Fa.

04:35.920 --> 04:38.190
I'm a huge failure as a coach.

04:45.480 --> 04:47.270
Because an excellent player

04:47.270 --> 04:48.950
I used to coach

04:50.510 --> 04:51.510
chose to

04:51.510 --> 04:53.560
end his life right in front of me.

04:59.430 --> 05:01.460
In the past, I only cared about winning

05:01.460 --> 05:02.990
and about football skills.

05:05.750 --> 05:08.150
So I really did neglect
his inner feelings.

05:10.070 --> 05:11.800
So much so that when he was

05:12.000 --> 05:13.430
suspected of doping,

05:15.070 --> 05:17.530
when he became
a target of public criticism,

05:20.720 --> 05:23.580
I wasn't a coach who
believed him unconditionally.

05:29.160 --> 05:29.960
Coach,

05:30.850 --> 05:33.120
when he faced all this,

05:33.140 --> 05:34.140
how old was he?

05:37.310 --> 05:38.120
Sixteen.

05:41.890 --> 05:43.450
A year younger than us now.

05:46.000 --> 05:48.060
Why are you suddenly telling us this?

05:51.720 --> 05:53.520
Because I want to tell you...

05:56.120 --> 05:57.070
not to give up.

05:59.440 --> 06:00.760
On the field,

06:02.310 --> 06:03.390
of course we can't

06:03.390 --> 06:05.600
give up the belief that we must win.

06:08.190 --> 06:09.360
But off the field...

06:13.950 --> 06:14.750
Boys,

06:16.040 --> 06:16.870
off the field,

06:16.870 --> 06:17.870
there are so many things

06:17.870 --> 06:20.240
far more important than football.

06:24.160 --> 06:25.120
So what I want to say is,

06:25.120 --> 06:27.000
no matter what you encounter,

06:29.920 --> 06:31.520
never give up on yourselves.

06:33.020 --> 06:34.240
Never give up on yourselves.

06:34.240 --> 06:35.840
Never give up on yourselves!

06:42.070 --> 06:43.390
From this moment on,

06:46.920 --> 06:48.380
I'll always be your coach.

06:52.720 --> 06:53.690
Believe that

06:54.920 --> 06:56.860
no matter what you encounter,

06:58.310 --> 07:00.370
I'll try my best to share your burden.

07:04.120 --> 07:06.040
And I'll never give up on you.

07:07.480 --> 07:08.920
If one day I'm gone,

07:11.390 --> 07:13.600
it's only because you're strong enough

07:13.600 --> 07:15.060
and don't need me anymore.

07:16.500 --> 07:17.960
I look forward to that day.

07:21.450 --> 07:22.840
I'm done.

07:25.430 --> 07:26.890
Class is over. Dismissed.

07:29.030 --> 07:30.890
Sorry for calling you out so late.

07:36.480 --> 07:37.680
Hurry back to sleep.

07:37.680 --> 07:39.210
We have training tomorrow.

07:56.360 --> 07:57.000
Coach.

07:59.490 --> 08:00.490
You still have us!

08:01.440 --> 08:02.440
See you tomorrow!

08:04.480 --> 08:05.480
-Yeah.
-See you tomorrow!

08:05.480 --> 08:07.480
-See you tomorrow, Coach!
-See you tomorrow, Coach!

08:07.480 --> 08:09.390
-We're here!
-See you tomorrow, Coach.

08:09.390 --> 08:10.790
See you tomorrow, Coach.

08:18.570 --> 08:19.950
♪ Time's passing by ♪

08:20.360 --> 08:21.160
See you tomorrow.

08:20.500 --> 08:22.580
♪ Nothing remains ♪

08:23.480 --> 08:26.230
♪ All the dreamers awake alone ♪

08:26.160 --> 08:27.510
See you tomorrow.

08:26.750 --> 08:28.500
♪ Shadows above ♪

08:29.240 --> 08:31.200
♪ Rain falls around ♪

08:31.530 --> 08:32.470
♪ In your arms ♪

08:33.140 --> 08:35.289
♪ We become one ♪

08:35.450 --> 08:37.840
Before he jumped off the roof,

08:37.870 --> 08:39.630
he must've struggled a lot.

09:08.320 --> 09:10.160
[Superstar Slacker]

09:36.630 --> 09:37.630
Ms. Ju Li?

09:40.120 --> 09:41.670
Wanxing isn't answering
my calls or messages.

09:41.670 --> 09:43.130
Do you know where she went?

10:10.560 --> 10:11.410
Lin Wanxing!

10:30.350 --> 10:31.630
Let's end it?

10:32.820 --> 10:34.670
Then let's end it.

10:34.690 --> 10:36.640
And I don't hope to see you again.

10:37.100 --> 10:38.960
Starting from the highest point,

10:39.270 --> 10:41.080
I can at least feel like
I'm flying for a few seconds.

10:41.080 --> 10:43.540
Split up
and look for tall buildings nearby.

11:12.760 --> 11:15.360
Heads: move forward.

11:16.120 --> 11:17.200
Tails:

11:17.870 --> 11:19.440
stay here.

12:16.150 --> 12:17.180
Lin Wanxing,

12:17.770 --> 12:19.770
good thing you backed out on it then.

12:35.530 --> 12:36.480
Lin Wanxing!

12:49.480 --> 12:50.320
Wang Fa.

12:51.810 --> 12:52.760
Lin Wanxing.

12:55.600 --> 12:57.120
Since you backed out on it,

12:58.140 --> 12:59.940
you should stick to it to the end.

13:05.630 --> 13:07.090
I was so worried about you,

13:07.210 --> 13:09.140
afraid you'd do something stupid.

13:32.750 --> 13:33.510
Don't worry.

13:34.490 --> 13:36.550
I wasn't going to do anything stupid.

13:37.910 --> 13:39.160
I wrote this postcard

13:39.620 --> 13:41.410
a year ago.

13:42.390 --> 13:48.070
♪ Waiting for a dark cloud
to pass by you ♪

13:42.670 --> 13:43.960
I came up here today

13:45.080 --> 13:46.550
just to get some fresh air

13:48.160 --> 13:49.970
and reflect on the past.

13:48.700 --> 13:53.520
♪ Listen closely to its cries ♪

13:53.670 --> 13:54.610
Really,

13:54.830 --> 13:56.040
I'm not lying to you.

13:55.310 --> 14:00.580
♪ The heavy rain will wash away
your reflection ♪

13:58.150 --> 14:00.750
After all, life is too precious

14:00.830 --> 14:02.500
to give up so easily,

14:01.240 --> 14:06.740
♪ And carry it toward distant scenery ♪

14:02.520 --> 14:03.370
right?

14:07.510 --> 14:09.200
Thank you for not giving up easily.

14:08.240 --> 14:14.140
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

14:14.690 --> 14:19.490
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

14:19.150 --> 14:21.160
Stay in the wind any longer,
and you'll catch a cold.

14:21.160 --> 14:26.310
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

14:21.360 --> 14:22.510
Let's go back.

14:23.000 --> 14:23.830
Wait.

14:27.290 --> 14:32.460
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

14:33.310 --> 14:39.090
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

14:39.920 --> 14:45.690
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

14:46.370 --> 14:51.980
♪ Let my tears be carried away,
back into the ocean ♪

14:50.600 --> 14:52.400
The wind is very gentle tonight.

14:52.830 --> 14:58.070
♪ And blown toward flowers
blooming far away ♪

14:52.910 --> 14:56.030
Let everything go with it.

14:59.380 --> 15:04.710
♪ I fill the blank spaces of life
with colors ♪

15:05.450 --> 15:11.190
♪ My dreams are not afraid to awaken;
they continue to exist ♪

15:09.270 --> 15:11.420
Finally, Wanxing has
someone protecting her.

15:11.420 --> 15:12.540
That's great.

15:11.970 --> 15:18.020
♪ I go beyond the dark clouds
and feel the haze disperse ♪

15:18.630 --> 15:24.330
♪ Let me understand myself more clearly ♪

15:24.630 --> 15:25.630
What's that sound?

15:25.550 --> 15:30.300
♪ Take away my reflection ♪

15:31.910 --> 15:38.870
♪ And go in search of distant scenery ♪

15:36.390 --> 15:37.120
It's so dirty.

15:37.120 --> 15:38.000
Don't eat that.

15:42.120 --> 15:43.550
Its leg is injured.

15:44.630 --> 15:45.960
It needs to go to the vet.

15:47.510 --> 15:48.370
I'll call a cab.

16:09.640 --> 16:11.190
Thank you for sending me back.

16:11.190 --> 16:11.880
Good night.

16:12.720 --> 16:13.270
Wait.

16:17.360 --> 16:18.400
Since you said

16:18.870 --> 16:19.800
good night to me,

16:21.020 --> 16:22.290
can I take it that

16:22.770 --> 16:23.900
you've forgiven me?

16:31.110 --> 16:32.440
My motives were impure.

16:33.390 --> 16:35.610
Approaching you and investigating you,

16:35.610 --> 16:37.210
it disappointed you, right?

16:42.600 --> 16:43.440
I admit that

16:44.510 --> 16:45.870
before, I did think

16:46.880 --> 16:48.000
we shouldn't

16:48.600 --> 16:49.950
stay in touch anymore.

16:50.110 --> 16:51.090
"Before"?

16:51.880 --> 16:52.840
What about now?

16:55.140 --> 16:56.570
During this time,

16:56.590 --> 16:57.920
I've thought a lot.

16:59.370 --> 17:00.830
It's understandable that

17:01.230 --> 17:02.490
you'd investigate me.

17:03.100 --> 17:04.690
If I were in your shoes,

17:05.310 --> 17:06.599
I'd have done the same.

17:08.099 --> 17:08.920
It's just...

17:08.920 --> 17:10.310
I clearly had so many chances

17:10.310 --> 17:11.589
to tell you the truth,

17:13.970 --> 17:14.880
but I didn't.

17:18.640 --> 17:19.770
It made you feel that

17:20.349 --> 17:21.810
I didn't really trust you.

17:22.960 --> 17:23.400
Right?

17:26.950 --> 17:29.010
But it wasn't that I didn't trust you.

17:30.380 --> 17:31.550
I was just afraid...

17:34.720 --> 17:36.180
Afraid you'd push me away.

17:39.510 --> 17:41.040
I didn't want you to hate me.

17:43.070 --> 17:45.470
But in the end,
I still ended up hurting you.

17:47.790 --> 17:48.590
I'm sorry.

17:54.270 --> 17:56.470
But if you're still willing to trust me,

18:00.030 --> 18:01.760
I'll hold nothing back from you

18:02.900 --> 18:04.110
from now on.

18:15.480 --> 18:17.540
You can be completely honest with me,

18:18.510 --> 18:19.770
but I can't do the same.

18:21.310 --> 18:22.840
There are still many things

18:23.240 --> 18:24.700
I don't want to talk about.

18:25.350 --> 18:26.030
It's OK.

18:27.810 --> 18:29.940
That sentence alone is honest enough.

18:35.590 --> 18:37.720
Demanding absolute trust from others

18:38.550 --> 18:40.610
while keeping things hidden myself,

18:41.200 --> 18:42.610
aren't you bothered by

18:42.790 --> 18:43.990
my double standards?

18:45.750 --> 18:47.680
You have the right to keep secrets.

18:59.200 --> 19:00.880
Is there anything else?

19:05.920 --> 19:06.880
It needs a bath.

19:07.480 --> 19:08.940
You can't handle it alone.

19:09.770 --> 19:10.850
I have a bathtub.

19:10.960 --> 19:11.960
It'll be easier.

19:13.830 --> 19:14.590
You...

19:15.920 --> 19:16.640
I can help.

19:36.600 --> 19:37.320
All done.

19:40.790 --> 19:41.580
Me too?

19:41.960 --> 19:43.090
Aren't you hurt too?

19:48.680 --> 19:50.160
Come, let me see.

19:50.160 --> 19:51.510
Does your paw hurt?

21:03.290 --> 21:04.820
Cover its eyes.

21:05.720 --> 21:06.200
OK.

21:06.200 --> 21:07.830
Make sure to wash behind its ears.

21:07.830 --> 21:09.430
It's been scratching there.

21:10.590 --> 21:13.390
Here, be good. Close your eyes.

21:13.790 --> 21:15.380
Close your eyes.

21:18.270 --> 21:20.130
You'll be fine once you're clean.

21:20.350 --> 21:20.810
Come on.

21:21.260 --> 21:21.950
Come here.

21:22.030 --> 21:24.640
Let's wash your little tummy.

21:24.640 --> 21:26.220
Wash your tummy...

21:28.620 --> 21:29.340
You...

21:29.370 --> 21:30.600
-I'm sorry.
-It's OK.

21:36.410 --> 21:37.770
Here, wipe yourself.

21:40.270 --> 21:41.310
This is...

21:41.790 --> 21:42.750
its towel.

21:45.310 --> 21:46.310
That's perfect.

21:47.400 --> 21:49.330
You can wipe yourselves together.

21:56.510 --> 21:58.000
Oh, it's shivering.

21:59.040 --> 22:00.280
Little doggy,

22:00.310 --> 22:01.750
you're actually white.

22:05.480 --> 22:06.440
Ms. Lin,

22:07.270 --> 22:08.720
let me adopt Ivory.

22:10.350 --> 22:11.680
Ivory?

22:11.680 --> 22:13.030
When did you name it?

22:14.400 --> 22:15.160
Just now.

22:16.830 --> 22:17.880
But...

22:18.550 --> 22:19.550
you don't look like

22:19.550 --> 22:21.720
someone who knows how to keep pets.

22:23.200 --> 22:23.960
So,

22:24.200 --> 22:25.970
I need you to help out.

22:29.830 --> 22:30.790
Well...

22:31.720 --> 22:33.270
There isn't much stuff at my place.

22:33.270 --> 22:35.130
Lots of room for it to move around.

22:40.450 --> 22:41.450
Alright then.

22:43.610 --> 22:44.810
Be good, Ivory.

22:44.840 --> 22:47.170
I'll come see you again tomorrow morning.

22:48.440 --> 22:49.270
Don't worry.

22:49.830 --> 22:51.380
I can report

22:51.570 --> 22:53.500
on its condition to you every day.

22:58.480 --> 22:59.680
Be good.

23:00.030 --> 23:01.480
You have to behave tonight,

23:01.480 --> 23:02.640
you hear me?

23:02.810 --> 23:04.340
I'll come see you tomorrow.

23:16.960 --> 23:18.070
Open the door!

23:19.200 --> 23:20.480
Wang Fa,

23:20.510 --> 23:21.640
open the door.

23:36.750 --> 23:38.720
Breakfast and daily necessities for Ivory.

23:38.720 --> 23:40.650
I grabbed you breakfast on the way.

23:42.310 --> 23:43.240
Let me do it. Go.

23:46.070 --> 23:48.030
Bacon, flatbread, fried dough sticks,

23:48.030 --> 23:50.760
egg yolk shumai, pork rib porridge,
and soy milk.

23:51.680 --> 23:53.550
Your "on the way"

23:53.550 --> 23:54.610
is quite the feast.

23:54.680 --> 23:55.750
Enjoy your meal.

23:55.750 --> 23:56.750
I'm going to work.

24:05.200 --> 24:06.300
I'll help you.

24:50.110 --> 24:51.640
What are you smiling about?

24:52.850 --> 24:53.980
I suddenly feel that

24:54.350 --> 24:55.960
being injured isn't so bad.

24:57.440 --> 24:59.480
The service fee will be
added to your rent.

24:59.480 --> 25:00.960
Bye-bye, Ivory.

25:06.350 --> 25:08.880
Bye-bye, Ivory.

25:20.400 --> 25:22.060
Speed up your cadence, Qin Ao.

25:25.240 --> 25:27.040
Make sure to lift your legs high.

25:27.160 --> 25:29.270
Fu Xinshu, remember to
breathe while running.

25:29.270 --> 25:29.920
Inhale for two steps,

25:29.920 --> 25:30.800
exhale for two steps.

25:30.800 --> 25:31.360
OK.

25:35.200 --> 25:36.860
Lin Lu, lift your legs higher.

25:37.310 --> 25:38.570
Speed up your cadence.

25:46.750 --> 25:47.880
Widen your stride.

25:55.400 --> 25:56.160
For you guys.

25:58.110 --> 25:58.790
Thanks.

26:03.690 --> 26:05.250
Ms. Lin went to a meeting.

26:07.300 --> 26:08.100
I know.

26:11.200 --> 26:12.460
What do you need me for?

26:15.500 --> 26:17.700
Thanks for finding Wanxing yesterday.

26:20.880 --> 26:23.080
You didn't just come to say that, right?

26:25.640 --> 26:28.300
I should've mentioned
that we grew up together.

26:31.480 --> 26:33.810
But actually,
I didn't like her much then.

26:34.880 --> 26:36.150
She was pretty,

26:36.170 --> 26:37.100
cute, polite,

26:37.710 --> 26:39.310
and even had good grades.

26:40.540 --> 26:42.400
Basically everyone liked her.

26:43.870 --> 26:46.820
She even had a fan club
on the school forum

26:47.550 --> 26:49.750
that recorded a lot of her preferences.

26:50.310 --> 26:51.680
Like how she

26:51.680 --> 26:52.960
doesn't like cilantro

26:54.730 --> 26:56.480
and loves the sweet and sour flavor.

26:56.480 --> 26:58.280
Sounds ridiculous, doesn't it?

27:00.240 --> 27:01.400
I can imagine.

27:04.720 --> 27:06.550
On the other hand, back then,

27:07.310 --> 27:08.830
I had super short hair,

27:08.990 --> 27:10.720
and because of my bad eyesight,

27:10.830 --> 27:12.270
I wore thick glasses.

27:13.400 --> 27:14.860
No one really talked to me.

27:17.000 --> 27:18.640
I remember once when

27:19.130 --> 27:20.390
I couldn't hold back,

27:21.310 --> 27:22.000
and I fought

27:22.000 --> 27:23.510
with the boy who loved to

27:23.510 --> 27:24.310
bully others.

27:25.240 --> 27:27.500
I beat him right into the nurse's office.

27:28.750 --> 27:30.400
But the homeroom teacher also punished me

27:30.400 --> 27:32.260
by making me stand in the hallway.

27:35.110 --> 27:37.840
Surprisingly, she came out
and stood with me too.

27:38.720 --> 27:40.780
I thought she just came to laugh at me.

27:42.030 --> 27:43.440
But she actually said,

27:45.160 --> 27:46.200
"You're so cool.

27:47.150 --> 27:49.250
Can I be in your group next PE class?"

27:53.720 --> 27:54.750
I got hurt here

27:54.750 --> 27:56.030
in that fight,

27:56.030 --> 27:57.230
and it kept bleeding.

27:57.550 --> 27:58.550
No one noticed.

27:59.480 --> 28:01.140
I didn't even realize myself.

28:02.750 --> 28:03.940
But she noticed.

28:06.030 --> 28:08.620
She was right there in the hallway,

28:08.790 --> 28:11.000
squatting down to put a bandage on me.

28:14.920 --> 28:16.920
After that, we became good friends.

28:18.640 --> 28:20.520
But then I transferred schools.

28:29.310 --> 28:31.110
Wanxing is very important to me.

28:36.510 --> 28:37.570
No less than to you.

28:42.830 --> 28:44.630
I care about Lin Wanxing at least

28:45.720 --> 28:46.650
as much as you do.

28:49.120 --> 28:50.400
Li, Wang Fa.

28:51.830 --> 28:54.290
The latest report
for the group stage is out.

29:06.970 --> 29:08.730
[Third round of the group stage]

29:07.170 --> 29:08.880
Chuncheng Xinpeng and Yuzhou Yinxiang

29:08.880 --> 29:10.200
played to a 2–2 draw.

29:10.590 --> 29:12.410
We beat Yinxiang.

29:12.580 --> 29:14.970
Yinxiang tied with Xinpeng.

29:15.030 --> 29:16.550
So it should be a piece of cake

29:16.550 --> 29:17.810
for us to beat Xinpeng!

29:18.920 --> 29:19.970
Did you see that

29:20.220 --> 29:22.030
Yongchuan Hengjiu beat Shenhai Yinbo

29:22.030 --> 29:23.240
by 9–0?

29:24.590 --> 29:27.110
Good thing our next opponent is Xinpeng.

29:27.220 --> 29:28.140
That's right.

29:28.480 --> 29:30.440
You still have room for improvement.

29:30.440 --> 29:33.110
We can still advance
by ranking second in points.

29:33.110 --> 29:34.400
Look at you two,

29:34.400 --> 29:35.510
so unambitious.

29:35.880 --> 29:37.920
We're not the noobs we used to be.

29:37.920 --> 29:39.440
Why can't we fight for first place?

29:39.440 --> 29:40.000
Exactly.

29:40.440 --> 29:41.840
What do you think, Coach?

29:43.240 --> 29:44.720
I think everyone can take a look

29:44.720 --> 29:45.850
at your recent data.

29:47.790 --> 29:48.590
Well,

29:48.590 --> 29:50.030
my high-intensity sprints

29:49.550 --> 29:51.370
[Player Name] [First Test] [Second Test]

29:50.030 --> 29:51.270
went from 15 to 25 reps.

29:51.270 --> 29:53.270
I finally won't hold everyone back.

29:54.240 --> 29:55.860
Still a bit behind me.

29:56.070 --> 29:58.170
Many moves that you couldn't do before

29:58.170 --> 29:59.690
can now be done

29:59.720 --> 30:01.120
due to improved stamina.

30:07.350 --> 30:08.460
So,

30:09.070 --> 30:10.480
our current data

30:11.400 --> 30:13.200
matches our current ambitions.

30:13.680 --> 30:14.740
We can fight for it.

30:15.090 --> 30:15.850
Fight for it!

30:16.510 --> 30:18.240
-Of course.
-Let's go then.

30:18.240 --> 30:20.000
Xinpeng's nothing!

30:20.000 --> 30:21.400
-Fight!
-Let's fight then.

30:21.400 --> 30:22.160
Fight for it!

30:35.790 --> 30:36.390
By the way,

30:36.600 --> 30:39.160
remember not to let Ivory lick its wound

30:39.160 --> 30:40.760
and feed it calcium tablets.

30:41.110 --> 30:42.070
I'm off.

30:42.350 --> 30:43.000
Wait.

30:44.310 --> 30:46.510
Aren't you going upstairs to see Ivory?

30:48.690 --> 30:50.350
It's time to change its dressing.

30:50.350 --> 30:51.560
I might not be able

30:51.730 --> 30:53.490
to handle it myself.

30:55.070 --> 30:55.600
Let's go.

30:59.790 --> 31:01.310
Be good, Ivory.

31:01.310 --> 31:03.240
Come, let me look at your wound.

31:04.720 --> 31:06.370
The wound is still a bit red.

31:06.400 --> 31:07.930
Let's apply some medicine.

31:08.310 --> 31:09.270
Hold him down.

31:09.270 --> 31:09.830
OK.

31:12.070 --> 31:13.480
Be good, Ivory.

31:13.480 --> 31:13.830
Good doggo.

31:13.830 --> 31:16.830
I'll give you beef jerky
after applying the medicine.

31:18.960 --> 31:20.270
It won't hurt, OK?

31:20.270 --> 31:21.240
It won't hurt.

31:22.880 --> 31:24.410
-Let me blow on it.
-Be good.

31:30.190 --> 31:32.260
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

31:32.740 --> 31:35.110
♪ On the summer night ♪

31:35.590 --> 31:41.100
♪ Like stars that glow so bright ♪

31:42.620 --> 31:44.880
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

31:45.590 --> 31:51.380
♪ Lost in a dream secretly ♪

31:54.760 --> 31:56.040
♪ With the evening breeze ♪

31:55.310 --> 31:56.960
You're blowing on my hair.

31:59.880 --> 32:00.630
Sorry.

32:02.830 --> 32:03.550
Ivory.

32:05.250 --> 32:06.260
Beef jerky.

32:12.720 --> 32:13.590
Go.

32:13.590 --> 32:14.270
Go play.

32:16.510 --> 32:18.750
Ivory was likely an abandoned dog,

32:18.930 --> 32:20.910
so he's traumatized.

32:21.920 --> 32:23.250
Spend more time with it.

32:24.000 --> 32:26.270
Dogs can also have PTSD?

32:31.670 --> 32:32.510
What's wrong?

32:34.640 --> 32:36.480
I think it has done a boo-boo.

32:41.070 --> 32:41.930
I'll handle it.

32:45.920 --> 32:46.790
It's getting late.

32:46.790 --> 32:48.270
I'll head back.

32:48.270 --> 32:50.400
Bye-bye, Ivory.

32:51.200 --> 32:52.590
Are you free this weekend?

32:52.590 --> 32:53.400
This weekend?

32:54.750 --> 32:55.680
I don't think so.

32:56.680 --> 32:58.110
Ivory needs a checkup.

32:58.110 --> 32:59.550
I can't handle it alone.

33:00.480 --> 33:01.740
Can't handle it again?

33:02.070 --> 33:03.200
Coach Wang,

33:03.440 --> 33:06.200
your hand is
getting worse with treatment, huh?

33:08.000 --> 33:10.270
No, just in case.

33:13.640 --> 33:16.070
Why do I feel like
you're trying to play me?

33:19.070 --> 33:20.070
You're mistaken.

33:23.870 --> 33:25.680
Right, there's one more thing.

33:25.710 --> 33:26.750
What is it?

33:26.800 --> 33:29.120
Are you booking me for
the following weekend?

33:29.120 --> 33:29.980
It's business.

33:33.110 --> 33:34.960
I want to show you something.

33:37.200 --> 33:38.030
What is it?

33:39.070 --> 33:42.200
Let's review the tapes of our game
with Yuzhou Yinxiang.

33:46.670 --> 33:47.990
Go back!

33:49.510 --> 33:50.830
Zheng Ren!

33:55.460 --> 33:56.880
Him! Go at him!

33:57.510 --> 33:58.830
Go at him!

34:01.550 --> 34:02.550
What do you think?

34:02.680 --> 34:03.750
I noticed that

34:03.750 --> 34:05.920
although Wen Chengye seems lazy sometimes

34:05.920 --> 34:06.830
and doesn't run much,

34:06.830 --> 34:08.070
at the crucial moment,

34:08.070 --> 34:10.199
he always does his part methodically.

34:12.510 --> 34:13.190
Look here.

34:13.960 --> 34:15.710
Our ball's been stolen,

34:15.710 --> 34:17.710
but Wen Chengye didn't chase it.

34:18.040 --> 34:19.400
Instead, he dropped to backcourt

34:19.400 --> 34:21.460
to mark their defensive midfielder.

34:21.639 --> 34:23.350
So you mean...

34:23.480 --> 34:24.330
He most likely

34:24.389 --> 34:25.929
anticipated it.

34:26.139 --> 34:28.639
He predicted they'd pass to
their defensive midfielder.

34:28.639 --> 34:31.610
So rather than wasting energy
chasing the ball,

34:31.639 --> 34:34.170
he thought about their next move
and prepared

34:34.800 --> 34:35.590
in advance.

34:36.230 --> 34:37.360
A very smart choice.

34:39.480 --> 34:41.600
Wen Chengye has brains

34:41.929 --> 34:43.170
and is bold enough,

34:43.400 --> 34:45.659
but he doesn't fit in with his teammates.

34:45.690 --> 34:46.620
You noticed, too,

34:46.620 --> 34:47.449
that on the field,

34:47.449 --> 34:49.130
he only plays by himself.

34:49.150 --> 34:50.670
Even when his teammates signal him,

34:50.670 --> 34:53.130
he only plays
according to his own judgment.

34:55.020 --> 34:56.100
So,

34:56.120 --> 34:58.210
he only seems to have joined us,

34:58.400 --> 35:00.710
but he has never really blended in.

35:00.920 --> 35:03.600
If he can build chemistry
with his teammates,

35:04.450 --> 35:06.250
it might elevate the whole team.

35:09.320 --> 35:10.850
I'll figure something out.

35:11.440 --> 35:12.190
Slow down.

35:12.190 --> 35:12.810
Nice one.

35:13.220 --> 35:14.200
-To Fu.
-Come on.

35:14.400 --> 35:15.400
Nice one!

35:15.670 --> 35:16.840
-Here you go!
-Go back!

35:16.840 --> 35:18.440
OK! Take a ten-minute break.

35:22.190 --> 35:23.030
Go there. Go.

35:49.880 --> 35:52.630
What do you think of Wen Chengye?

35:54.800 --> 35:55.880
He is

35:55.880 --> 35:58.110
a bit hard to approach.

35:58.670 --> 36:01.320
But you can tell
he likes playing football.

36:02.710 --> 36:04.030
I think so too.

36:05.670 --> 36:07.920
Fu Xinshu, I have a little plan

36:07.920 --> 36:09.070
to help Wen Chengye

36:09.070 --> 36:10.870
integrate into the team better.

36:10.960 --> 36:11.820
Care to join me?

36:12.190 --> 36:13.070
Of course.

36:14.920 --> 36:16.590
Why did Ms. Lin call us up here?

36:16.590 --> 36:17.670
-I don't know.
-Where is she?

36:17.670 --> 36:18.440
I don't know.

36:18.460 --> 36:19.730
It's a bit cold today.

36:20.110 --> 36:20.960
Come on up.

36:20.960 --> 36:22.070
Ms. Lin!

36:22.070 --> 36:23.200
-Ms. Lin.
-I'm here.

36:23.880 --> 36:25.630
-Ms. Lin!
-Ms. Lin.

36:25.630 --> 36:26.550
Go, go, go!

36:30.590 --> 36:31.550
Ms. Lin.

36:33.790 --> 36:36.270
Ms. Lin, what are you up to now?

36:36.290 --> 36:38.820
Calling us up here
to catch a cold in the night?

36:40.760 --> 36:41.760
Is everyone here?

36:42.960 --> 36:43.480
Today,

36:43.480 --> 36:44.760
we're going to solve

36:44.760 --> 36:46.390
a very serious problem.

36:46.420 --> 36:49.250
According to the latest
Dietary Guidelines for Chinese Residents,

36:49.250 --> 36:51.380
our football team's late-night meals

36:51.400 --> 36:52.470
are very poor.

36:53.760 --> 36:54.840
How are they poor?

37:00.360 --> 37:01.190
I propose

37:01.630 --> 37:03.030
a ban on instant noodles.

37:03.480 --> 37:05.880
-W-Wait! No way!
-No way.

37:05.880 --> 37:07.630
-I'm so hungry at night.
-What will we eat then?

37:07.630 --> 37:09.800
Besides, we're in a tournament now.

37:09.800 --> 37:11.000
We have extra training every day,

37:11.000 --> 37:12.190
and the cafeteria is closed after.

37:12.190 --> 37:13.840
-There's nothing else to eat.
-Yeah.

37:13.840 --> 37:15.840
But instant noodles lack nutrition.

37:15.840 --> 37:17.110
You have matches coming up.

37:17.110 --> 37:18.910
Instant noodles aren't enough.

37:19.760 --> 37:21.160
Does anyone second this?

37:23.960 --> 37:25.480
We always eat instant noodles at night.

37:25.480 --> 37:27.740
Even three or four packs
don't fill me up.

37:30.000 --> 37:31.330
One vote to second this?

37:31.720 --> 37:33.840
Now, let's vote.

37:40.280 --> 37:42.440
But instant noodles are
tasty and convenient.

37:42.440 --> 37:44.510
What else can we eat at night?

37:44.510 --> 37:45.590
That's easy.

37:45.590 --> 37:46.840
We can cook ourselves.

37:46.840 --> 37:48.880
It's not like
you haven't tasted my cooking.

37:48.880 --> 37:50.390
Your food's actually a bit too greasy.

37:50.390 --> 37:52.960
-Your food makes our muscles shrink.
-I'll just eat instant noodles.

37:52.960 --> 37:54.280
Why don't you consider the cost?

37:54.280 --> 37:55.400
Where do we get so much money?

37:55.400 --> 37:55.840
Right.

37:55.840 --> 37:59.070
To have a balanced diet and build muscle,

37:59.070 --> 38:00.840
we need to have green and organic stuff.

38:00.840 --> 38:02.840
Your standards are too high.

38:02.840 --> 38:04.480
Can we meet them?

38:04.480 --> 38:05.400
It's possible.

38:06.440 --> 38:07.630
We can grow our own vegetables.

38:07.630 --> 38:09.710
-Grow our own?
-Who knows how to?

38:09.710 --> 38:11.960
-How can we grow our own?
-Grow them? Where?

38:11.960 --> 38:13.480
With such a big place,

38:13.480 --> 38:15.320
can't we grow some vegetables?

38:15.320 --> 38:16.960
Growing your vegetables
and cooking yourselves,

38:16.960 --> 38:19.420
all the things you just said
can be achieved.

38:20.670 --> 38:23.960
So, prospering through self-sufficiency
by starting up

38:23.960 --> 38:25.490
a little vegetable garden!

38:25.840 --> 38:27.800
We can grow tomatoes.

38:28.360 --> 38:30.630
Let's appoint a person in charge
of the vegetable plot.

38:30.630 --> 38:32.090
It'll be easier to manage.

38:33.760 --> 38:34.800
Wen Chengye,

38:34.960 --> 38:36.380
can you be in charge?

38:39.000 --> 38:40.550
It's decided, Wen Chengye.

38:40.550 --> 38:41.520
Do you agree?

38:41.630 --> 38:42.880
If you don't agree,

38:42.880 --> 38:45.940
how about joining
Ms. Ju's physics competition class?

39:05.780 --> 39:07.070
♪ Time's passing by ♪

39:07.730 --> 39:09.620
♪ Nothing remains ♪

39:10.510 --> 39:12.230
-Tomatoes.
-Tomatoes? OK.

39:10.710 --> 39:13.280
♪ All the dreamers awake alone ♪

39:13.980 --> 39:15.680
♪ Shadows above ♪

39:15.800 --> 39:16.840
How about baby bok choy?

39:16.470 --> 39:18.180
♪ Rain falls around ♪

39:18.230 --> 39:20.590
It's easy to store when it grows up,

39:18.760 --> 39:19.590
♪ In your arms ♪

39:20.390 --> 39:21.850
♪ We become one ♪

39:20.590 --> 39:22.390
and you can eat it all year round.

39:22.640 --> 39:24.300
♪ Through day and night ♪

39:22.760 --> 39:23.560
Bok choy then.

39:23.960 --> 39:24.510
OK.

39:25.040 --> 39:27.070
♪ I can see you ♪

39:28.380 --> 39:30.460
♪ In my eyes ♪

39:28.550 --> 39:30.400
Go, go, go!

39:30.400 --> 39:32.110
-Let's get to work.
-Come on, let's start.

39:31.220 --> 39:32.690
♪ Just hold me tight ♪

39:33.530 --> 39:38.740
♪ Look into my soul so deeply ♪

39:33.840 --> 39:35.230
Go, go, go.

39:35.400 --> 39:37.000
Pour the soil in first.

39:38.070 --> 39:38.920
Come on!

39:38.920 --> 39:40.590
Fertilizer! Fertilizer!

39:39.480 --> 39:41.230
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

39:40.590 --> 39:41.630
Lin Lu.

39:42.070 --> 39:43.000
Chen Jianghe.

39:42.080 --> 39:43.130
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

39:43.000 --> 39:44.070
-OK.
-OK.

39:44.070 --> 39:44.880
Zhi Hui.

39:44.130 --> 39:45.140
♪ Wonderful days ♪

39:46.120 --> 39:47.560
♪ Are so close to me ♪

39:48.520 --> 39:49.690
♪ Memories fly ♪

39:49.360 --> 39:50.760
Stir it like this, right?

39:50.590 --> 39:51.840
♪ Leave them all behind ♪

39:50.760 --> 39:51.280
Yes.

39:51.280 --> 39:53.070
Is fertilizer white?

39:52.850 --> 39:58.450
♪ Just take my hand and stay with me ♪

39:53.070 --> 39:54.400
Yes, yes.

39:58.030 --> 40:00.070
Wen Chengye,
how much fertilizer do I add?

40:00.070 --> 40:00.840
Two spoons are enough.

40:00.840 --> 40:01.510
Two spoons.

40:02.480 --> 40:04.150
Wen Chengye, is this enough water?

40:04.150 --> 40:04.880
Wait, I'm coming.

40:04.880 --> 40:05.230
What's this?

40:05.230 --> 40:06.070
Do I add more water?

40:05.670 --> 40:06.970
♪ Time's passing by ♪

40:06.070 --> 40:07.600
Is it OK to stir it like this?

40:07.630 --> 40:09.530
♪ Nothing remains ♪

40:07.840 --> 40:08.190
Yes.

40:08.190 --> 40:10.660
Wen Chengye, we should
add fertilizer here, right?

40:10.660 --> 40:13.220
♪ All the dreamers awake alone ♪

40:13.550 --> 40:14.670
Ms. Lin.

40:13.980 --> 40:15.620
♪ Shadows above ♪

40:15.210 --> 40:16.110
Well,

40:16.110 --> 40:17.630
Coach is injured,

40:16.370 --> 40:18.160
♪ Rain falls around ♪

40:17.630 --> 40:19.280
so it's fine that he doesn't help.

40:18.660 --> 40:19.490
♪ In your arms ♪

40:19.280 --> 40:20.520
But you...

40:20.290 --> 40:21.790
♪ We become one ♪

40:20.630 --> 40:23.030
Me? What about me?

40:22.540 --> 40:24.170
♪ Through day and night ♪

40:23.030 --> 40:25.320
I'm the investor of this little garden.

40:24.940 --> 40:26.970
♪ I can see you ♪

40:25.320 --> 40:28.280
Have you ever seen investors
getting their hands dirty?

40:28.280 --> 40:30.360
♪ In my eyes ♪

40:30.720 --> 40:32.690
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

40:32.800 --> 40:33.760
Stir it a bit more.

40:33.330 --> 40:34.600
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

40:33.760 --> 40:34.230
It's still dry.

40:34.230 --> 40:35.710
-Be gentle!
-Slowly.

40:35.370 --> 40:36.500
♪ Wonderful days ♪

40:36.320 --> 40:37.280
I'm tired.

40:37.360 --> 40:38.800
♪ Are so close to me ♪

40:39.000 --> 40:39.880
Guys...

40:39.760 --> 40:40.930
♪ Memories fly ♪

40:41.360 --> 40:42.230
I found some seeds

40:41.830 --> 40:43.170
♪ Leave them all behind ♪

40:42.230 --> 40:43.560
suitable for planting.

40:44.090 --> 40:50.590
♪ Just take my hand and stay with me ♪

40:46.190 --> 40:48.360
-Let me see.
-A pot of Chinese eggplants.

40:48.360 --> 40:50.440
I want these scallions.

40:50.920 --> 40:51.920
Wen Chengye.

40:51.940 --> 40:52.940
Wen Chengye!

40:53.280 --> 40:55.480
What are these two bags without labels?

40:55.960 --> 40:56.800
Let me see.

40:58.000 --> 40:59.400
The light yellow ones are
Facing Heaven hot peppers.

40:59.400 --> 41:00.800
This should be bell peppers.

41:00.800 --> 41:02.860
You can always count on a top student.

41:04.000 --> 41:04.800
Come on.

41:05.840 --> 41:07.000
Let me help you.

41:10.150 --> 41:11.630
Looks like your instruction is

41:11.630 --> 41:12.760
making great progress.

41:12.760 --> 41:13.670
Of course.

41:14.280 --> 41:15.740
Everyone must be thirsty.

41:15.920 --> 41:16.670
Have some drinks.

41:16.670 --> 41:17.510
Yogurt for everyone.

41:17.510 --> 41:18.280
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

41:18.280 --> 41:19.840
-It's sweet and sour.
-Thanks, Ms. Lin!

41:19.840 --> 41:22.480
-Here, here.
-Thanks, Ms. Lin!

41:22.480 --> 41:23.920
Divide it yourselves.

41:23.920 --> 41:25.150
-Lu, get me one.
-So good. One more.

41:25.150 --> 41:25.960
Here, here.

41:25.960 --> 41:26.880
Have two.

41:26.880 --> 41:27.670
Another one.

41:28.150 --> 41:29.360
Come on!

41:29.360 --> 41:31.190
The watering begins!

41:42.530 --> 41:43.810
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

41:45.000 --> 41:46.330
♪ Because you're with me ♪

41:49.480 --> 41:50.630
♪ The light shimmers ♪

41:52.180 --> 41:53.240
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

41:55.090 --> 41:56.150
♪ Running towards you ♪

41:57.110 --> 41:58.300
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

41:57.320 --> 41:58.800
Come on!

41:58.800 --> 41:59.860
Let's take a photo.

42:02.150 --> 42:03.130
♪ Walk side by side ♪

42:02.260 --> 42:03.090
Ready?

42:03.120 --> 42:04.610
Wait! Hang on!

42:03.760 --> 42:06.080
♪ Become ourselves ♪

42:07.800 --> 42:09.480
Wen Chengye!

42:08.110 --> 42:09.050
♪ Amid the storm ♪

42:09.850 --> 42:14.290
♪ As our breaths slowly intertwine ♪

42:10.290 --> 42:10.800
Hurry!

42:10.800 --> 42:12.110
Don't be such a loner!

42:12.110 --> 42:12.960
Hurry up.

42:13.360 --> 42:14.840
Three, two, one!

42:14.840 --> 42:15.960
♪ Heartbeats alternating ♪

42:14.840 --> 42:16.900
Cheese!

42:16.180 --> 42:21.220
♪ A chemistry about to emerge ♪

42:21.800 --> 42:23.110
♪ The stars are shining ♪

42:23.210 --> 42:28.400
♪ Take my hand and run forward ♪

42:29.000 --> 42:30.140
♪ For you ♪

42:30.340 --> 42:35.640
♪ I'm willing to
keep practicing and practicing ♪

42:39.010 --> 42:40.180
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪
